tr: box in which a corpse is buried or cremated

value.def: A coffin is a box in which a dead body is buried or cremated.
If you say that one thing is a nail in the coffin of another thing, you mean that it will help bring about its end or failure.

example.ex: A fine would be the final nail in the coffin of the airline.
example.tran: 罚款将会是对这家航空公司的最后致命一击。

value.tran: 促使…失败（或完结）的因素
